@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title How you pay with coins and get change

start
:You want to buy a toy for 45;
:Look in your jar for coins;
:Pick a 30 coin and a 20 coin
(that is 50, enough);
:Hand both whole coins to the shop;
:Shop keeps 45 for the toy
and 2 for the helper fee;
:You get a brand-new 3 coin back
as change;
note right
  Coins in (50) = coins out (48)
  plus the fee (2).
end note
:Your old 30 and 20 coins are gone
for good and cannot be used again;
stop
@enduml
